OL,3,C'You go in a boy and come out a man':
OL,4,CVeteran shares D-Day journey
OL,6,FPaul Crone spoke to Richard about his
OL,7,Fmemories of D-Day, and his journey
OL,8,Fthrough Europe.
OL,10,FA 100-year-old D-Day veteran has
OL,11,Fshared his journey from storming the
OL,12,Fbeaches of Normandy to being one of
OL,13,Fthe first British soldiers to witness
OL,14,Fthe horrors of a Nazi concentration
OL,15,Fcamp.
OL,17,FRichard Brock, who is believed to be
OL,18,Fthe last surviving member of his
OL,19,Fbattalion, was 20 when he made the
OL,20,Ftrip from his home in to Portsmouth
OL,21,Ffor the D-Day assault.
