OL,3,C'You go in a boy and come out a man':
OL,4,CVeteran shares D-Day journey
OL,6,FOn one occasion, a fighting patrol
OL,7,Fmade up of from Richard's battalion
OL,8,Fwere sent out to scout ahead.
OL,10,FTheir bodies were found the next
OL,11,Fmorning, all killed by German
OL,12,FSchmeisser machine guns.
OL,14,FRichard said: "With the Schmeisser's
OL,15,Fthey put the empty magazines on the
OL,16,Fbody, so when we advanced we saw them
OL,17,Fthere."
